---
import ImageComparisonSlider from './ImageComparisonSlider.astro';
---

<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
  <ImageComparisonSlider
    baseImageSrc="/images/profile-pixel.webp"
    overlayImageSrc="/images/profile.webp"
    baseImageAlt="Pixelated Profile picture"
    overlayImageAlt="Regular Profile picture"
    initialPosition={33}
    sliderWidth="w-56 sm:w-64 md:w-72 lg:w-80"
    sliderHeight="h-56 sm:h-64 md:h-72 lg:h-80"
    instructionText="Slide to view grayscale image"
  />
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
  <p>
    Hey there! 👋🏼 I'm Alex, a data science undergraduate and pursuing AI research @ Harvard working
    on a 3D computer vision foundation model for cellular and molecular biology.
    🧬
  </p>
  <p>
    Previously, I interned as a SWE, MLE, and data scientist at Microsoft,
    Boeing, Edwards Lifesciences, and AI startups (including an MIT CSAIL
    spinoff), gaining hands-on experience in developing scalable AI products.
    I'm passionate about driving innovation and making a meaningful impact
    through technology that benefits humanity. 🚀
  </p>
  <p>
    Feel free to reach out and connect—I look forward to collaborating and
    sharing ideas!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  @keyframes slideAnimation {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateX(-10px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateX(10px);
    }
  }

  .slide-animation {
    animation: slideAnimation 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
</style>